text: Super Wings (Korean: 출동! 슈퍼윙스; Chinese: 超级飞侠) is a South Korean animated television series produced by FunnyFlux Entertainment in South Korea and distributed by Alpha Group Co., Ltd. in China, and Little Airplane Productions in the United States and It aired broadcasting to Sprout/Universal Kids to on March 14, 2015 and until 2021, with the production support from the Educational Broadcasting System in South Korea, and additional support from KOCCA.
